        "subject": "LU-16314 osd-ldiskfs: Migrate %p to %pK",
        "message": "LU-16314 osd-ldiskfs: Migrate %p to %pK\n\nMigrating to %pK which works in all the supported\nkernels.\n\nA couple of passes of:\n\ngrep -rl '[^a-zA-Z%]%p[^a-zA-Z]' |\n  xargs -i{} sed -i -E 's/([^a-zA-Z%])%p([^a-zA-Z])/\\1%pK\\2/g' {}\n\nAlso fixes white space around the affect code change\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10945\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ia89631cf0663c91bd139ab76bd7e7502b3f305ff\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
